rewrite using threads instead of processes

parent should create 7 threads
0 read input file, init stations to 0
1 station 0
2 station 1
3 station 2
4 station 3
5 station 4
6 write output

remove pipes
add array of queues of P_Record, one per stage + output (6 total)

when a product rcord is ready to be sent to a station, enqueue it to its queue

